data.description: Check out this spacious 4 bedroom home with 3 bathrooms! This is an amazing opportunity for anyone looking to upsize. Bonus room located in the basement that could be used as a bedroom or office space! With over 3000 square feet of finished space you will surely have enough room to grow. Kitchen is fully equipped with refrigerator, dishwasher, over the range microwave, and stove. Large living area downstairs features a fireplace and french doors that lead to a private patio. Outside the dining room doors you'll find a large deck and pool that would be perfect for entertaining. Newer roof installed in 2020 along with gutters and gutter guards. Sellers are willing to remove pool if desired by buyers. Sellers are willing to pay $3000 to buyers closing cost that can be used to buy down rate! You don't want to miss this one! Contact your agent for a private viewing!
